Statistics of recipients of subsistence payments

Until 2004: Federal Act on Public Assistance.

2003: Introduction of basic security benefits in old age and
in cases of reduced earning capacity.

2005: Replacement of the Federal Act on Public Assistance by
the Social Code, Book XII.

2005 and 2006: Excluding Bremen.
